    <item>
      <title>马斯克的特朗普交易让特斯拉成为赢家，市值上涨 5700 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/musk-s-trump-trade-makes-tesla-a-winner-with-570-billion-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[不到两个月前，特斯拉公司股价即将迎来这家电动汽车制造商上市十五年以来第三年亏损。但经过过去七周的强劲上涨，该股突然成为标普 500 指数 2024 年表现最好的股票之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/musk-s-trump-trade-makes-tesla-a-winner-with-570-billion-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 13:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
